@baseUrl = http://localhost:5062/api

### Send sensor data from Device 1 (Lettuce Unit)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sensor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "macAddress": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:01",
  "ph": 6.2,
  "tds": 950,
  "waterTemperature": 22.5,
  "airHumidity": 68.0
}

### Send sensor data from Device 2 (Lettuce Unit)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sensor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "macAddress": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:02",
  "ph": 5.8,
  "tds": 1100,
  "waterTemperature": 23.1,
  "airHumidity": 72.0
}

### Get dashboard data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/latest

### Get device history (24 hours)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/history/1?hours=24

### Manual control - Turn pump ON
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/actuator/control
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "macAddress": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:01",
  "actuatorType": 0,
  "action": "ON",
  "controlType": 1,
  "reason": "Manual pump activation for testing"
}

### Manual control - Turn fan OFF
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/actuator/control
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "macAddress": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:01",
  "actuatorType": 1,
  "action": "OFF",
  "controlType": 1,
  "reason": "Manual fan deactivation"
}

### Get actuator logs for device 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/actuator/logs/1?days=7
